T|Novi|0|Situation: sb connection unavailable — no live sl snapshot, post, or cr data cld be queried. From project state: IG baselines (followers, engagement rate, Reels reach) remain "[not yet recorded]" across all metrics. Last ka analytical sn was April 15, 2026, which flagged an engagement rate drop — status of that flag is unresolved. SS26 cg prep is in-flight (ln + at), targeting late June launch, but no launch date has been confirmed by Stark. The metrics table that ka is supposed to own is effectively empty — every signal-dependent KPI (ROAS target, Reels vs. static allocation, cn mix op) is waiting on a baseline that has not been established.
