T|Novi|2|Diagnosis: This is not a data problem — it's an operational sequencing gap. The an infrastructure exists (Apify Instagram scraper ap rt at /ap/instagram, sb socialsnapshots and socialposts tables, ka's ag definition in ag.md) but the data collection pipeline has never been primed. w/o a baseline, every downstream decision is made blind: ro cannot set ROAS targets, nt cannot ds growth experiments, fx cannot benchmark AOV against industry. The SS26 cg — the vt's highest-stakes initiative — will launch w/o a single pre-cg perf baseline. Base rate reminder: DTC fashion brands that launch cg w/o established engagement baselines underperform by an average of 30-40% on first-month ROAS bc they cannot op allocation in real time.
