T|Hour|2|Diagnosis: This is a sequencing problem, not an an gap. ka cannot produce intelligence from nothing — the role is downstream of pd, pricing, and onboarding. The ct path for hb is: (1) fx completes the runway al and pricing md recommendation (HRB-002), (2) Stark approves pricing, (3) dv builds the trial-to-paid funnel (HRB-001), (4) first cohort enters the funnel. Only at step 4 does ka's analytical fn activate. Until then, ka's highest-value contribution is structural readiness: ensuring the an sc, dashboards, and alert thresholds are defined so that when the first us lands, measurement is immediate — not retroactive.
